  <div>


    <div class="card shadow " style="width: 18rem;">
      <img src="assets/rezerocard.jpg" class="card-img-top  w-100" alt="..." style="height: 200px;">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World-

        </h5>
        <p class="card-text">When Subaru Natsuki leaves the convenience store, the last thing he expects is to be wrenched from his everyday life and dropped into a fantasy world. Things aren't looking good for the bewildered teenager. </p>
        <%= link_to "Read More", readln_rezero_path, class:"btn btn-primary w-100"  %>

      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card mt-5 shadow " style="width: 18rem;">
      <img src="assets/slime tensei.jpg" class="card-img-top w-100" alt="..." style="height: 200px;">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime
        </h5>
        <p class="card-text">Now, liberated from the mundanities of his past life, Rimuru embarks on a fresh journey with a distinct goal in mind. As he grows accustomed to his new physique, his gooey antics ripple throughout the world. </p>
        <%= link_to "Read More", readln_slime_path, class:"btn btn-primary w-100"  %>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="d-flex  " >
  
    <div>
      <div class="card shadow " style="width: 18rem;">
        <img src="assets/konosuba.jpg" class="card-img-top  w-100" alt="..." style="height: 200px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">KonoSuba: God's Blessing on This Wonderful World!</h5>
          <p class="card-text">After dying a laughable and pathetic death on his way back from buying a game, high school student and recluse Kazuma Satou finds himself sitting before a beautiful but obnoxious goddess named Aqua.</p>
        <%= link_to "Read More", readln_konosuba_path, class:"btn btn-primary w-100"  %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mt-5 shadow " style="width: 18rem;">
        <img src="assets/overlord card.jpg" class="card-img-top  w-100" alt="..." style="height: 200px;">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Overlord</h5>
          <p class="card-text">The final hour of the popular virtual reality game Yggdrasil has come. However, Momonga, a powerful wizard and master of the dark guild Ainz Ooal Gown, decides to spend his last few moments in the game as the servers begin to shut down.</p>
        <%= link_to "Read More", readln_overlord_path, class:"btn btn-primary w-100"  %>
        </div>
